      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW CORNELIUS (1) had the drop on the lead before drawing clear to score (25.19) at Shepparton in Grade 4/5 over 450m. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to his name from three starts. In form and can go on with it. PAW WAVERLY (3) produced a modest effort most recently when fifth at Shepparton over 450m behind Dewana Star (25.54) in a Special conditions H. Placed at her previous run. Leading chance. PAW FARINA (2) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at his last four runs. Last start finished 3rd in a Grade 5 on March 19 over 450m at Ballarat behind Bush Big Show beaten 4 lengths (25.46). Well placed and gets his chance. ASTON CASTLE (8) is a last start winner worth following up.",
